                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5647" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1427</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9898 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化升级：服装代工企业海思堡如何涅槃重生？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital Upgrade: How does the Apparel Foundry Company HaiSiBao Reborn?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王节祥，刘盈伶，夏季</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东海思堡(尚牛智能)服装服饰集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服装代工企业；数字化转型；智能制造；平台化；2021百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Apparel Foundry Companies; Digital Transformation; Intelligent Manufacturing; Platformization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型被认为是服装产业减少库存、降本增效的重要举措，但是企业如何推进数字化转型仍是战略迷思。本案例讲述了海思堡集团从一个传统服装代工企业转型成为具备大规模定制能力的智能制造企业，并尝试搭建服装产业互联网平台的故事。海思堡首先通过培育自主能力、借助外部赋能的方式推进制造数字化；随后在消费侧搭建具备自主品牌的C2M平台，与各大电商平台展开合作，增加订单；最后在供给侧搭建ASPOP产业互联网平台，对外输出工厂改造能力，强化产能。订单越多、改造的产能越多，以此构建起一个供需高效匹配的服务平台。但是，如何让平台的“飞轮”运转起来，挑战巨大。本案例旨在引导学员思考传统制造企业如何在数字化浪潮下突围，并把握从智能生产企业向产业互联网服务平台转型发展的机会。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Digital transformation is considered as an important method for the apparel industry to reduce inventory and costs while increase efficiency, but how companies promote digital transformation is still a strategic mystery. This case tells the story of HaiSiBao&#39;s transformation from a traditional clothing OEM company to an intelligent manufacturing company with mass customization capabilities, and its attempt to build a clothing industry internet platform. First, HaiSiBao promoted the digitalization of manufacturing by cultivating autonomous capabilities and relying on external empowerment. Second, HaiSiBao built a C2M platform with its own brand on the consumer side, and cooperate with major e-commerce platforms to increase orders. Third, on the supply side, HaiSiBao built the ASPOP industry internet platform to export factory transformation capabilities and strengthen production capacity. The more orders, the more production capacity transformed. As a result, the service platform will efficiently matches two sides. However, how to make the &quot;flywheel&quot; of the platform work is a huge challenge. The purpose of this case is guiding students to think about how traditional manufacturing companies can achieve breakthroughs under the wave of digitization, and grasp the opportunities for transformation from intelligent production companies to industry internet service platforms.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产业升级 数字化转型创新与平台战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
